<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als gmeiner reichs stett
                                <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>, die nehst nach
                            <expan>ost<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu Ulme bey
                            <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan> warn, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> von der <expan>unpillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        newekeit, die ir von der unterkewffel <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> bey ewch
                                <expan>angefang<ex>en</ex></expan> habt,
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und ir in mit
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>umb</expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> habt, in <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> antwurt wir niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan>, daz ir das meynet
                                <expan>abczulass<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns fremd und
                                <expan>unpillich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> dunket. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                        ewr <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, ir wellet sölich unpillich
                        newekeit abtun und uns und die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> bey altem
                                <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>herkome<ex>n</ex></expan> bey ewch <expan>beleibe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> wol <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                        Das <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>willikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> und <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>, wan ir wol
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>steen</expan> mugt, daz uns und den
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> sölich sache niht wol zuleiden
                                <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan>. Und lat uns
                            <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr frewntlich
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey disem botten.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
